{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6b44b9a5-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s569b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"569b"},"text":"§ 569b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contracts; architect and engineering services; surveying and mapping services","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Contracts for architect and engineering services, and surveying and mapping services, shall be awarded by the Chief of Engineers in accordance with title IX of the Federal Property and Administrative Services Act of 1949.","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002020"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002020"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id6b44b9a6-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/63/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–63, title I","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-07-30"},"text":"July 30, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/311"},"text":"97 Stat. 311","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id6b44b9a7-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id6b44b9a8-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id6b44b9a9-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Federal Property and Administrative Services Act of 1949, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-06-30/ch288"},"text":"act June 30, 1949, ch. 288","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/377"},"text":"63 Stat. 377","children":[],"tail":". Title IX of the Act, which was classified generally to subchapter VI (§ 541 et seq.) of chapter 10 of former Title 40, Public Buildings, Property, and Works, was repealed and reenacted by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/217"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–217","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1, 6(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-08-21"},"text":"Aug. 21, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/1062"},"text":"116 Stat. 1062","children":[],"tail":", 1304, as chapter 11 (§ 1101 et seq.) of Title 40, Public Buildings, Property, and Works. For disposition of sections of former Title 40 to revised Title 40, see Table preceding "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t40/s101"},"text":"section 101 of Title 40","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
